        <briefdescription>
<para>Updates text components with current game timer values. </para>
        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>For each matching entity, compares the timer revision against the observer&apos;s cached revision. On mismatch, formats the elapsed/remaining time via the TimeFormatterComponent and updates the UiTextComponent.</para>
